          { "feature": "known_ckd_as_risk_factor", "weight": 4 },
          { "feature": "normal_k_with_baseline_medication", "weight": 3 }
        ],
        "management": "Stop or dose reduce causative medication. Check for co-contributing factors (NSAIDs, high K diet, volume depletion). Consider adding SZC or patiromer to allow continuation of ACEi/ARB if indicated (e.g., heart failure, CKD with proteinuria). Monitor K closely."
      },
      {
