          { "feature": "thrombocytosis_or_leukocytosis", "weight": 3 },
          { "feature": "repeat_sample_shows_normal_k", "weight": 5 }
        ],
        "management": "No treatment needed. Repeat sample (heparinized, no tourniquet, rapid processing). Consider ABG sample with direct measurement. Correct underlying cause (hemolysis, extreme thrombocytosis)."
